alerts.title: Flood Warning
alerts.description: ...A FLOOD WARNING FOR A DAM FLOODGATE RELEASE REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 300 AM MST MONDAY FOR MARICOPA COUNTY... At 412 PM MST, water released from Granite Reef Dam has allowed elevated flow down the Salt River between the aforementioned dam and Tempe Town Lake. Roads built into the river channel in this area have been inundated with water.
